    <name>T-Story 110%</name>
    <summary>Tetris-style falling blocks puzzle with with a story</summary>

    <description>
        <p>
            T-Story is a free, open-source tetris-style falling-blocks arcade puzzle for Linux.
            It features crisp visuals, responsive controls, energetic music, and an
            efficient engine inspired by classic handheld tetris gameplay.
        </p>
        <p>
            Play solo or up to 3 players locally with keyboard, mouse, or USB/Bluetooth
            controllers. Includes strong computer A.I. opponents and multiple game modes
            in this modern tetris tribute.
        </p>
    </description>

    <launchable type="desktop-id">io.github.savantsavior.t-story.desktop</launchable>

